## Animation Strategy (GSAP + ScrollTrigger)

| Element | Animation | Trigger |
|---------|-----------|---------|
| Hero heading | Split-text reveal, letters animate up | Page load |
| Hero stats | Fade up + stagger | Page load (delayed) |
| Particles | Continuous float | Always active |
| About quote | Fade in from bottom | Scroll into view |
| About bio | Slide up | Scroll into view |
| Stack icons | Stagger fade-in | Scroll into view |
| Experience rows | Slide in from left | Scroll into view |
| Project rows | Slide up + stagger | Scroll into view |
| Project hover | Others dim to 30% | Mouse hover |
| Contact email | Scale up | Scroll into view |
| Custom cursor | Follow mouse, expand on hover | Always active |

